column1: Baby Barnaby's////Green eggs were delicious.   Many comment on them being "wet"
column2: but I think that's more from the cheese mixed in than the eggs being undercooked at all.  I found them to be delightful
column3: and I don't like wet scrambled eggs.  I thought the chicken sausage it comes with to be good as well.  There were tons of potatoes
column4: and they were fine.  Coffee was very good too
column5: and I like that they leave a small carafe of it on your table.
